children.text:
# Psoriasis Area Severity Index (PASI)

The PASI is an index used to express the severity of psoriasis. It combines the severity (erythema, induration and desquamation) and percentage of affected area.

children.label: Percentage of head and neck affected
children.name: percentage_of_head_and_neck
